  "commit_message": "solver: speed-up setup phase (#52487)\n\nModifications:\n* Cache base `AspFunction` instances in `_AspFunctionBuilder` so\nrepeated use of `fn.some_name` reuse the same object. This is safe\nbecause `__call__` always returns a new instance.\n* Add `__iter__` to `DisjointSetOfValues`\n* Cache `__str__` for `ImmutableSpec`\n\nSigned-off-by: Massimiliano Culpo <massimiliano.culpo@gmail.com>",
